column5: I wish there was the "secret to a successful team" in there.
its strange they wouldnt take photos of the items...but then again...maybe they want people to pay to see them...
Of course they're gonna make people pay to see what they found... either that or maybe they'll put the box on Jen's new desk in the renovated building and we can all drop in and view the stuff there!
That's pretty cool, photos would be cooler.

Just saw it on the news they showed some pics of what they found which included NHL Rulebooks from the time as well as some newspapers and this small ivory elephant quite bizarre not sure if that was everything or if there is more to come.  Kawartha Kev
The local and national tv news had images tonight.
